        <div class="note">
            <p class="noteInDiv" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #f6861f;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;"> By default, <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet14">TM </MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet16">and </MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet15">MT&#160;</MadCap:conditionalText>suggestions are applied in the current target language, but you can apply them in all target languages.  You can change your language settings in the Project Properties dialog. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Interface/UI_Elements/Project_Properties_Dialog_Lingo.htm">Project Properties Dialog</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
            <p>If you choose to pre-translate your project during project creation, <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet14">TM&#160;</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet16">and </MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet15">MT&#160;</MadCap:conditionalText>suggestions are applied to the whole project across all languages, regardless of the setting in the Project Properties dialog.</p>
